WEBVTT

01:34.260 --> 01:35.716
Your family?

01:37.010 --> 01:39.387
Can you tell me anything about them?

01:42.220 --> 01:44.097
I don't want to talk about it.

01:46.480 --> 01:50.553
That's okay.
We can talk about something else.

01:51.900 --> 01:53.310
Like what?

01:53.980 --> 01:58.735
Like, what was
your favourite subject in school?

02:01.830 --> 02:03.070
Music.

02:03.870 --> 02:05.189
Favourite food?

02:08.370 --> 02:09.621
Pizza.

02:13.340 --> 02:15.661
What about least favourite food?

