02:28.440 --> 02:31.398
bread crumbs and onions, grilled in a pan.

02:31.520 --> 02:33.147
Ugh.

02:33.230 --> 02:35.027
Oh, that sounds terrible.

02:37.360 --> 02:40.409
Spend your whole life swimming upstream,
end up a patty.

02:42.370 --> 02:45.328
Yeah. Should've swam the other way.

02:45.950 --> 02:47.702
Yeah, should've.

03:00.590 --> 03:03.639
