nobody goes outside the range.

07:17.220 --> 07:18.630
We did, but this is a special case.

07:18.730 --> 07:20.379
The kid can't look for her family
on her own.

07:20.480 --> 07:21.515
We have to do it for her.

07:21.600 --> 07:23.261
