Well, you should come and help me look.

08:49.110 --> 08:51.317
Well, I've got a turnip situation.

08:52.110 --> 08:55.068
- Don't you get bored in here?
- I do, yeah. It's great.

08:55.160 --> 08:56.366
It is.

08:56.450 --> 08:58.156
You wanna just stare at a wall later?

08:58.240 --> 08:59.195
- Deal.
- Yes.

08:59.280 --> 09:01.282
