13:59.330 --> 14:03.255
Still never asked her
why she helped me after what I did.

14:07.510 --> 14:08.465
Ask her.

14:14.560 --> 14:17.723
Hey. What are you doing?

14:19.310 --> 14:20.641
Nothing.

14:23.730 --> 14:25.982
It's okay.
They haven't been gone that long.

14:30.280 --> 14:32.077
I know it wasn't a regular run.

14:35.040 --> 14:36.359
Well, look, we didn't want to tell you

14:36.450 --> 14:38.247
because we didn't
want you to get your hopes up.

14:38.330 --> 14:41.242
But if your family is out there,
we'll find them.

14:42.340 --> 14:43.796
Why don't you ever go out there?

14:44.670 --> 14:46.376
'Cause I like it better in here.

14:46.460 --> 14:49.588
Now, you gonna help me
with those puke turnips?

15:12.870 --> 15:14.656
Mom, did you find anything?

15:14.780 --> 15:16.691
Don't.

15:16.790 --> 15:17.745
Mom?

15:18.710 --> 15:19.995
Now, turn around.

15:26.250 --> 15:29.048
Your keys. Hand them over.

15:36.390 --> 15:37.675
You don't have to do this.

15:38.390 --> 15:39.470
The keys.

15:51.150 --> 15:52.356
Shit.

15:56.410 --> 15:59.493
We have a settlement. Strong walls.

16:00.620 --> 16:04.283
Plenty of food. Good people.

16:04.750 --> 16:06.411
It's the truth.

16:07.460 --> 16:09.121
We just took in a kid.

16:11.130 --> 16:15.544
Says she's from around here somewhere.
A little girl.

16:18.560 --> 16:21.518
Named Charlie? You know her?

16:21.600 --> 16:23.648
I don't have a kid.

16:26.230 --> 16:27.970
