16:42.830 --> 16:43.706
It's okay.

16:53.930 --> 16:55.079
Easy there.

17:01.520 --> 17:02.384
Wait!

17:05.190 --> 17:06.054
Madison!

17:10.320 --> 17:12.390
Please, put it down.

17:17.530 --> 17:20.192
We're not gonna hurt you.
You can trust us.

17:21.580 --> 17:23.901
You need help? Hell, you need the car.
We'll give it to you.

17:29.340 --> 17:30.375
Don't...

17:46.350 --> 17:48.477
It's okay! We'll get you out!

17:48.900 --> 17:50.015
Get the hatch open.

18:12.340 --> 18:14.080
It's rusted shut.

18:15.720 --> 18:17.256
- Stay close.
- I'm trying!

18:28.810 --> 18:30.892
Good, good, good. Push, push.

19:20.610 --> 19:21.656
Mom?

19:55.110 --> 19:59.103
Madison, who on God's Earth did we risk
life and limb to save this time?

20:02.320 --> 20:05.733
