when she had me at gunpoint.

20:07.450 --> 20:08.826
Hey.

20:10.660 --> 20:12.457
No one's gone til! they're gone.

20:16.630 --> 20:17.995
Naomi.

20:20.420 --> 20:21.967
My name is Naomi.

20:25.600 --> 20:29.593
I'm sorry. I wasn't going to hurt you.

20:33.850 --> 20:36.057
Well, somebody led them into the tank.

20:37.270 --> 20:38.680
Any idea who?

20:40.030 --> 20:43.272
I just camped there last night.
I'm not from here.

20:43.360 --> 20:45.237
Where are you from?

20:49.370 --> 20:54.490
It's been a long time
since I've been from anywhere.

20:56.710 --> 20:58.371
You've been travelling this whole time?

20:58.460 --> 21:00.291
The whole time.

21:11.060 --> 21:14.689
We should leave. Now.

21:52.720 --> 21:54.597
- We gotta do something.
- Like what?

21:54.680 --> 21:58.935
I don't know, go out there and figure out
where that music came from.

21:59.020 --> 22:01.853
Maybe it was something to do with
why they're not back yet.

22:01.940 --> 22:04.932
You know,
maybe it was them trying to signal us.

22:05.030 --> 22:08.238
Look, I know you're worried
about your family,

22:08.320 --> 22:12.654
but let's just wait,
see if we hear it again.

22:32.970 --> 22:34.676
I need you to open the gate.

22:36.180 --> 22:37.636
I can do that.

23:25.360 --> 23:27.180
Easy.

24:14.820 --> 24:15.980
Nick, get back here.

24:30.130 --> 24:31.791
Nick, what are you doing?

24:33.090 --> 24:34.751
You know, just taking a stroll.

24:34.840 --> 24:37.638
What happened to you?

24:38.350 --> 24:39.760
Get in.

24:56.950 --> 24:58.941
Charlie, can we talk for a second?

25:01.750 --> 25:03.490
It's okay.

25:04.710 --> 25:06.826
I know you didn't find them.

25:10.170 --> 25:11.205
I'm sorry.

25:17.850 --> 25:21.172
I've gotta ask you another
question, though. It's not an easy one.

25:24.140 --> 25:28.395
What happened at your camp?
Do you know who did that?

25:39.030 --> 25:41.328
We can talk about it another time.

25:49.290 --> 25:51.918
- Thanks.
- Least I could do.

25:54.510 --> 25:56.250
Are you a nurse or a doctor?

25:57.220 --> 25:58.255
Nurse.

25:59.890 --> 26:00.925
What kind?

26:03.350 --> 26:07.844
Last answer. No more questions.
ER, then ICU.

26:15.070 --> 26:17.061
Hey, how'd she take it?

26:17.150 --> 26:18.981
I don't think it was a surprise.

26:20.030 --> 26:22.407
All right, I'll go check on her.
Thank you.

26:30.080 --> 26:33.379
You didn't tell me your camp
was a baseball stadium.

26:33.460 --> 26:35.291
You didn't believe I had a camp.

26:39.260 --> 26:42.343
- How many people live here?
- Forty-seven.

26:43.510 --> 26:45.421
Forty-eight, if you decide to stay.

26:49.850 --> 26:52.603
I pulled a gun on you.

26:54.530 --> 26:56.100
But you didn't shoot.

26:59.280 --> 27:02.659
I've done a lot worse
when I was out there. We all did.

27:04.620 --> 27:07.532
I thought I lost my kids for good
because of it.

27:11.420 --> 27:13.081
But I found them.

27:14.380 --> 27:19.500
And then we found this place,
and we built it up, together.

27:20.840 --> 27:23.968
We are who we are because of it.

27:26.310 --> 27:27.800
You don't even know me.

27:30.100 --> 27:31.727
And you don't know us.

27:33.860 --> 27:35.930
So, we're both taking a chance.

27:42.820 --> 27:44.481
I know it's a lot.

27:47.500 --> 27:49.650
Why don't you see how you feel
after a shower?

27:54.630 --> 27:55.915
A shower?

27:56.000 --> 27:57.206
Uh-huh.

27:58.670 --> 28:00.126
- Is the water--
- Yeah.

28:00.220 --> 28:03.178
But you gotta turn the knob all the way
to the right to get it really hot.

28:14.690 --> 28:16.897
Hit them if they get within 50 feet of us.

28:19.740 --> 28:21.310
Copy.

28:24.530 --> 28:28.409
You know, I could've helped you guys
out there if he'd let me come along.

28:30.410 --> 28:33.823
I don ’t think thats why
