he doesn't want to get to know me.

28:38.210 --> 28:40.371
It might be the other way around.

28:41.260 --> 28:43.672
Does he really think
that's going to stop me?

28:47.600 --> 28:48.919
Luce?

28:55.690 --> 28:58.727
You guys need to get inside right now!

28:58.820 --> 29:00.890
