31:50.070 --> 31:52.652
You picked one hell of a night to join us.

32:47.250 --> 32:48.160
There a problem?

32:50.130 --> 32:53.679
We're good. You want one?

32:56.760 --> 33:00.594
We got a lot of people inside
with a lot of guns.

33:00.680 --> 33:02.386
That's a hell of a welcome.

33:03.730 --> 33:07.018
We saw what you did
to that camp by those tanks.

33:08.270 --> 33:09.601
You think we did that?

33:09.690 --> 33:11.567
Well, your flag was flying over it.

33:11.650 --> 33:16.519
Yeah. Because _we had to
clean up their mess.

33:17.370 --> 33:19.076
